{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund support for veterans and patients facing prescription opioid dependency",
        "additional_details": "Many people are trapped in a cycle of dependency, and want to access help but can\u2019t. The Government must provide more funding to ensure more people can be helped.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to fund dedicated, non-stigmatised detox and withdrawal support specifically for patients who have become dependent on opioids, such as Tramadol, through legitimate medical prescriptions.",
